name: FREAKARRANCUDO!
description: This big and hot guy is called FREAKARRANCUDO and was hired by the fishermen and sailors of FREAKOLAND to scare away the evil spirits and bring luck to their fishing trips.In exchange he received food, drink, coins, and other items. As the years went by, the fishermen ended up disbelieving in the evils of the rivers of FREAKOLAND and FREAKARRANCUDO ended up unemployed. Fortunately, he is smart and has saved his gold coins, so that he could live comfortably for many years, although he does not like to be idle. One day while watching war movies on TV, he realized that he had a new opportunity and could easily be a stuntman. He traveled to Hollywood where he trained with the best and ended up even being a stuntman for famous names like Harnold Schazweger, Silvestre StaAlone , Jean Claudio Von Dime and Curt Russell He has a deep voice and would make a great musical duo with FREAKOLOCO! #36. / Type: Creature / Edition: 3rd / Alignment: Chaotic Good / Height: 205 cm / Weight: 135 kg / Strength: 78 / Dexterity: 25 / Constitution: 70 / Intelligence: 12 / Wisdom: 30 / Charisma: 25
